a:2:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"list";a:5:{i:0;a:62:{s:5:"wr_id";s:2:"20";s:6:"wr_num";s:3:"-18";s:8:"wr_reply";s:0:"";s:9:"wr_parent";s:2:"20";s:13:"wr_is_comment";s:1:"0";s:10:"wr_comment";s:1:"0";s:16:"wr_comment_reply";s:0:"";s:7:"ca_name";s:0:"";s:9:"wr_option";s:10:"html1,mail";s:10:"wr_subject";s:21:"Beta 1.0 Major update";s:10:"wr_content";s:1627:"<p>Dear Friends,</p>

<p>it&#39;s been a long time.</p>

<p>Hirediversity has been reorganized.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>1.&nbsp; Upgraded the main page,</strong></p>

<p>&nbsp; Most of the commet&nbsp;about the site were about design, have it&nbsp;got a little better?</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>2. Security upgrade</strong><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;We&#39;ve done an SSL upgrade. We always value privacy the best.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>3. Sign in with&nbsp;Facebook</strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>4. Enhance notification function</strong><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;- We can forward more important information to you in the future.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong><span style="color:#27ae60;">The SKK GSB MBA office</span></strong> helped <strong><span style="color:#2980b9;">Hirediversity team</span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;further.</p>

<p><span style="color:#27ae60;"><strong>The SKK GSB MBA</strong></span> has agreed that the issues <span style="color:#2980b9;"><strong>Hirediversity</strong></span> want to address at are&nbsp;socially important.</p>

<p>Thanks to the contribution of <span style="color:#27ae60;"><strong>SKK GSB MBA</strong></span>, <span style="color:#2980b9;"><strong>Hirediversity</strong></span> was able to steadily deliver&nbsp;value to our friend&nbsp;without considering any profit.</p>

<p>Let us all thank the<span style="color:#27ae60;"><strong> SKK GSB MBA.</strong></span></p>

<p><br />
&nbsp;</p>

