wr_comment";s:1:"0";s:16:"wr_comment_reply";s:0:"";s:7:"ca_name";s:6:"Update";s:9:"wr_option";s:5:"html1";s:10:"wr_subject";s:33:"Beta 0.6 Reputation Check service";s:10:"wr_content";s:1344:"<p>Dear friend.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>I&#39;m glad to be able to offer you a new service.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Many foreign friends raised the issue of the <u><strong>difficulty of getting information about Korean companies</strong></u>.</p>

<p>Since foreign applicants hard to&nbsp;get information about the company,</p>

<p>There were problems like this.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>1. Poor interview pass rate<br />
2. Failure to negotiate salary properly<br />
3. Fraud (especially via SNS)</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>We opened the <span style="color:#3498db;">Reputation Check service</span> to solve this problem.&nbsp;</p>

<p><br />
It&#39;s simple.<br />
You can send a recruitment notice&nbsp;from&nbsp;the company you want to apply for to</p>

<p>Check@hirediversity.club</p>

<p>(You can send me a link, a capture or a file.)</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Then we will send you a <span style="color:#3498db;">Reputation check report</span>.&nbsp;<br />
It&#39;s easy and comfortable, isn&#39;t?</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Letter from the friend who used this service already</p>

<p><a href="http://hirediversity.kr/Community/7">http://hirediversity.kr/Community/7</a></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
