pdates HAS 2.0";s:10:"wr_content";s:1390:"<p>Hi guys</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Hirediversity Beta 0.5 started!</strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>In this update, we have added content to help you get the job <u>you want most</u>.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>HAS 2.0 (Hirediversity apply system)</p>

<p><br />
If the applicant has an interview with HAS, we will send you&nbsp;the materials to prepare for the interview.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Interview preparation contents may include</p>

<p><u>interview questions from past year and answers of successful applicants</u>,</p>

<p><u>The industry trends in Korea in which the company belongs.</u></p>

<p><u>Tips</u></p>

<p>which are agreed in advance with the company.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Is intended to ensure equal opportunities for foreign applicants in regards to obtaining the interview preparation materials; as they have limited resources compared to the Korean Applicants</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>I was actually very surprised. This is because these materials are easily available for Korean applicants.</p>

<p>However, there are not many foreign applicants who know this.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Companies have agreed to our story and more and more companies will be adopting HAS 2.0 in the future.</p>

<p>Wish you success!</p>
