<br />
I am delighted to be able to bring you new news. This update has <strong>3</strong> changes.<br />
&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>1. </strong><strong>Hirediversity</strong><strong>&nbsp;Apply System.</strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>There is a hard point in order to apply to Korean companies.</p>

<p>You have to write a &quot;자기소개서&quot; and join a KOREAN job search site.</p>

<p>And most of the information requested by Korean job sites are not suitable for foreigners.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>We have created a <span style="color:#27ae60;">&quot;</span><span style="color:#27ae60;">Hirediversity</span><span style="color:#27ae60;"> Apply System&quot;</span> to solve this problem.</p>

<p>If you find &quot;apply@hirediversity.club&quot; in &quot;How to apply&quot;, you should be glad.</p>

<p>Because it means that the company adopt <span style="color:#27ae60;">&quot;</span><span style="color:#27ae60;">Hirediversity</span><span style="color:#27ae60;"> Apply System&quot;</span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>The advantage of this system is</p>

<p><br />
1. You do not have to make &quot;자기소개서&quot; and other things not suitable for foreigners.<br />
&nbsp;</p>

<p>2. Companies that use this system are willing to hire foreigners very much.</p>

<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;(Maybe you can have&nbsp;a much better chance to be hired)</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>3. More and more companies are asking us for &quot;recommendation&quot;, and this system will be the beginning.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>2. Community</strong><br />
&nbsp;</p>

<p>The reason we make &quot;Community&quot; is because of the HR staff&#39;s needs.<br />
HR representatives want to communicate with potential applicants,</p>

<p>but there is currently no method to communicate with foreign applicants.</p>

<p>It&#39;s sad.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>By sharing your information through the community, it will probably be the best way to promote you to HR representatives.</p>

<p>I promise the community will be getting more and more developed.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>We&#39;ve made it possible to share information with each other through the community.</p>

<p>Through this, you can share information and help others.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>3. RSS&nbsp;</strong></p>

<p>Through RSS you can subscribe to job announcements coming up.<br />
<br />
What is RSS and What can I do with it?</p>

<p>-&nbsp;https://www.digitaltrends.com/computing/what-is-an-rss-feed/</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
